No. —, Original.

Submitted February 25, 1907. Mr. George W. Watt and Mr. James M. Dohan for petitioner. Mr. Joseph H. Choate, Jr., opposing.

Ex parte: In the Matter of John Armstrong Chanler, Petitioner.

Decided March 4, 1907.

Motion for leave to file petition for a writ of prohibition denied.
